item.title: Spotify's Year in Music: Drake Most Streamed Artist, Major Lazer & DJ Snake Had Top Song | Billboard
item.description:
Spotify's Year in Music: Drake Most Streamed Artist, Major Lazer & DJ Snake Had Top Song | Billboard

Spotify unveiled its annual Year in Music results on Tuesday, with Drake topping a crowded field to become the world's most streamed artist. The rapper had over 1.8 billion streams and 46 million listeners. The year's most streamed female artist was Rihanna, with over 1 billion streams and 57 million listeners.

item.title: Martin Shkreli Says He's Trying To Bail Out Bobby Shmurda
item.description:
Martin Shkreli Says He's Trying To Bail Out Bobby Shmurda

Two of the most intriguing Hip Hop tales of the past year have just collided head on. Pharma-douche Martin Shkreli - who pissed off the world once again by buying the rights to the mysterious Wu Tang album Once Upon a Time in Shaolin - says he's working to bail out Bobby Shmurda.
